## 2026-04-03 - GeneratorService.executeGenerator overwrites concurrent generator updates
- Fixed race condition in `executeGenerator`: the original code read `current = this.generators.get(id)` at L603 (sync), then awaited `tokenStore.resolveToken()` at L608, then wrote `{ ...current, ... }` at L611 вҖ” any concurrent `update()` call during the await was silently overwritten because `current` was stale.
- Fix: moved the `this.generators.get(id)` read to AFTER all awaits, right before `this.generators.set()`. The `lastRunSourceValue` fallback now uses `current.lastRunSourceValue` (from the fresh re-read) instead of the pre-await stale snapshot.
- Files changed: `packages/server/src/services/generator-service.ts` ~L600-620

